<taxonomicNameLabel id="A2755797B758FFA3C004CD6E3B96FA12" box="[1122,1185,1404,1430]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
They share the sclerotized plate in internal sac (
<figureCitation id="13092A7BB758FFA3C6D4CDB63C2FFA3A" box="[690,792,1444,1470]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 ­ 10" captionStartId="4.[264,383,1831,1855]" captionTargetBox="[355,1246,605,1809]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[352,1252,603,1813]" captionText="FIGURES 1 ­ 10: Male genitalia. 1 ­ 2: Plateros kalamensis sp. n.; 3 ­ 4: P. m a m a s e n s i s sp. n.; 5 ­ 6: P. milenae sp. n.; 7 ­ 8: P. orobuensis sp. n.; 9 ­ 10: P. tanatorajensis sp. n. Scale 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/155511/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
Figs 
<number id="3DFA24D9B758FFA3C689CDB63DC9FA3A" box="[751,766,1444,1470]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" value="3.0">3</number>
­6
</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="13092A7BB758FFA3C743CDB63C73FA3A" box="[805,836,1444,1470]" captionStart="FIGURES 11 ­ 27. 11 ­ 13" captionStartId="5.[264,383,1721,1745]" captionTargetBox="[348,1240,494,1701]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[343,1242,494,1704]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 11 ­ 27. 11 ­ 13: Male genitalia. 11: Plateros rubromamasensis sp. n.; 12 ­ 13: P. lalui sp. n.; 14 ­ 19: Male pronota. 14: P. kalamensis sp. n.; 15: P. mamasensis sp. n.; 16: P. milenae sp. n.; 17: P. orobuensis sp. n.; 18: P. rubromamasensis sp. n.; 19: P. tanatorajensis sp. n.; 20: Female antenna. 20: P. flavidus Kleine, 1933; 21 ­ 27: Male antennae. 21: P. kalamensis sp. n.; 22: P. lalui sp. n.; 23: P. mamasensis sp. n.; 24: P. milenae sp. n.; 25: P. orobuensis sp. n.; 26: P. rubromamasensis sp. n.; 27: P. tanatorajensis sp. n. Scale 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/155512/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">11</figureCitation>
). Additionally 
<taxonomicName id="4C324D7DB758FFA3C790CDB63BD3FA39" authority="Tvardik &amp; Bocak, 2001" authorityName="Tvardik &amp; Bocak" authorityYear="2001" box="[1014,1252,1444,1469]" class="Insecta" family="Lycidae" genus="Plateros" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubromamasensis" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis id="B946EAECB758FFA3C790CDB63BD3FA39" box="[1014,1252,1444,1469]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">P. rubromamasensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A2755797B758FFA3C08DCDB63A1DFA3A" box="[1259,1322,1444,1470]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C324D7DB758FFA3C55DCDDE3ED0FA61" authority="Tvardik &amp; Bocak, 2001" authorityName="Tvardik &amp; Bocak" authorityYear="2001" box="[315,487,1484,1509]" class="Insecta" family="Lycidae" genus="Plateros" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mamasensis" status="sp. n.">
